{"lemma":"أَهِلَّة","slug":"أَهِلَّة","root":"ه.ل.ل","root_slug":"ه-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ه-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَهِلَّة","root":"هلل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1436","n1437"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%90%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crescent, crescent moon","examples":[{"text":"يَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلْأَهِلَّةِ ۖ قُلْ هِيَ مَوَاقِيتُ لِلنَّاسِ وَٱلْحَجِّ ۗ وَلَيْسَ ٱلْبِرُّ بِأَن تَأْتُوا الْبُيُوتَ مِن ظُهُورِهَا وَلَٰكِنَّ الْبِرَّ مَنِ ٱتَّقَىٰ ۗ وَأْتُوا ٱلْبُيُوتَ مِنْ أَبْوَابِهَا ۚ وَٱتَّقُوا ٱللّٰهَ لَعَلَّكُمْ تُفْلِحُونَ","english":"They ask thee about the crescents. Say: \"They are fixed seasons for mankind and for the pilgrimage\". It is not righteousness that ye go to houses by the backs thereof, but the righteous man is he who wardeth off. So go to houses by the gates thereof, and observe your duty to Allah, that ye may be successful."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"moonlight, glow, aura"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a surname"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate with Hebrew ה־ל־ל (“Forming words relating to being clear and shining”, root) and Ugaritic 𐎅𐎍𐎍 (hll)."},"ipa":["/hi.laːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1436","headword_ar":"اَهْلَةٌ","root":"Ahl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholN","text_ar":"اَهْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places:       -A2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ahlapN","text_ar":"اَهلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n1437","headword_ar":"اَهِلَةٌ","root":"Ahl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlN","text_ar":"مَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: so in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahumo laA^aholu A^ahilapK","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُمْ لَاَهْلُ اَهِلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K) [app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily they are sojourners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settlers, possessed of property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholN","text_ar":"اَهْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"here signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuluwlN","text_ar":"حُلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAl~N","text_ar":"حَالٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (JK, TA.) [But] Yoo says that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo A^aholu A^aholapi","text_ar":"هُمْ اَهْلُ اَهْلَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ahilapK","text_ar":"اَهِلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are people of the distinguished sort."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","K"]}]}}